content: The ethics review board has been formed. Now to ensure our project not only enhances cognition but does so responsibly. It's a complex balance.
AI tools have made our project development process more robust. We've avoided another potential setback. The simulation might be glitching, but we're adapting.
Meeting with the privacy-focused startup was productive. We're aligning our cognitive project with their privacy framework. This could be a game-changer.
